# #  Raspberry Pi Audio Config Dokumentation

##  Systeminformation
- **Raspberry Pi Model:** Pi 4B
- **OS:** Raspberry Pi OS (Bookworm)
- **Ljudsystem:** PipeWire + RAOP (AirPlay)

